author: philip
msg: Fix issue 1943.  Track added directories during dry-run merges to
allow the corect notification to be output.
* subversion/libsvn_client/diff.c
(struct merge_cmd_baton): Add const char* added_path element.
(merge_file_added): Set changed state if path is a child of
added_path.
(merge_dir_added): Set changed state if path is a child of
added_path.  Set added_path if adding and path is not child
of added_path.
(svn_client_merge, svn_client_merge_peg): Init added_path.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/merge_tests.py
(add_with_history): Remove workaround for old buggy behaviour.
